Tris Coffin https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tris_Coffin 0 Tristram Chockley Coffin (August 13, 1909 – March 26, 1990) was a film and television actor from the latter 1930s through the 1970s, usually in westerns or other action-adventure productions.
